OL,3,CWhy Starmer may fight on despite
OL,4,CLabour's worst election predictions
OL,6,FAs election results become clearer on
OL,7,FFriday afternoon from sports halls and
OL,8,Fcommunity centres across England,
OL,9,FScotland and Wales - a consistent
OL,10,Ftheme is predicted: devastating losses
OL,11,Ffor Labour.
OL,13,FOne of the main reasons for that
OL,14,Fprediction? The Labour Party is
OL,15,Ftelling us it will happen.
OL,17,FLabour's expectation management for
OL,18,Fthese May elections has been in the
OL,19,Fworks since the start of the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
