OL,3,CWhy Starmer may fight on despite
OL,4,CLabour's worst election predictions
OL,6,FIn England, party activists are braced
OL,7,Ffor at least one thousand councillors
OL,8,Fto lose their seats. In Scotland and
OL,9,FWales, no Labour member thinks the
OL,10,Fparty has any real chance of winning
OL,11,Fthe most seats.
OL,13,FKeir Starmer's team hope that having
OL,14,Ftold its MPs to expect a dreadful set
OL,15,Fof results, the party is prepared for
OL,16,Fthe worst.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
