OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778101867
OL,3,CWhy Starmer may fight on despite
OL,4,CLabour's worst election predictions
OL,6,FBut the sight of Green mayors taking
OL,7,Fcontrol of authorities run by Labour
OL,8,Ffor decades, of Reform beating the
OL,9,Fparty in Wales, of councillors who've
OL,10,Fgiven years of service to the Labour
OL,11,Fmovement booted out of office in
OL,12,Fpunishment for performance of the
OL,13,FWestminster government - all of this,
OL,14,Fif borne out, could trigger emotions
OL,15,Feven the most hardy Labour veterans
OL,16,Fmight struggle to control.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
