OL,3,CWhy Starmer may fight on despite
OL,4,CLabour's worst election predictions
OL,6,FLabour staffers have been dispatched
OL,7,Fto the election counts most likely to
OL,8,Fdeal the heaviest blows to the party
OL,9,Fon Friday, in the hope of persuading
OL,10,Ffurious and newly-unemployed
OL,11,Fcouncillors to steer clear of TV
OL,12,Fcameras.
OL,14,FHow all of this will play out over the
OL,15,Fcoming weekend is the great unknown.
OL,16,FWill any Labour MPs issue fresh calls
OL,17,Ffor a change of prime minister? Will
OL,18,Fany cabinet ministers feel compelled
OL,19,Fto speak out?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
