OL,3,CWhy Starmer may fight on despite
OL,4,CLabour's worst election predictions
OL,6,FThe various Labour leadership hopefuls
OL,7,Fwill be watching and waiting every
OL,8,Fmoment. Plans have been sketched out -
OL,9,Fbut there are signs nobody is ready to
OL,10,Fpush the button just yet.
OL,12,FWhen you talk to people close to the
OL,13,Fvarious contenders - Angela Rayner,
OL,14,FWes Streeting and Andy Burnham - all
OL,15,Fmake sure to ask questions about what
OL,16,Ftheir rivals are planning. Nobody
OL,17,Fwants to be the first to go over the
OL,18,Ftop, but nobody wants to miss out if a
OL,19,Fcontest is triggered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
