OL,3,CWhy Starmer may fight on despite
OL,4,CLabour's worst election predictions
OL,6,FThe fundamental obstacles that stopped
OL,7,Fa leadership challenge to Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fin February - it's not the right time
OL,9,Ffor any candidate and there's no
OL,10,Fconsensus on who it should be - remain
OL,11,Fthis May.
OL,13,FEd Miliband said back then that Labour
OL,14,FMPs "looked over the precipice" and
OL,15,Fchose to support Keir Starmer.
OL,17,FBackbenchers know they only have one
OL,18,Fshot at changing the leader in this
OL,19,Fparliament, and they want to make sure
OL,20,Fthey get it right.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
